depending on \code{shortage_action}.

Three design modes are supported. In \code{"augmented"} mode, all treatments are
unreplicated; the function identifies which ones have sufficient seed for a
single plot and flags the rest for exclusion. In \code{"p_rep"} mode, a subset of
treatments is selected for replication at \code{desired_replications} and the
remainder are unreplicated; selection is governed by \code{priority}, restricted
